```

**Required Monthly Costs (Production):**

| Component | Size | Type | Rate | Monthly | Annual |
|-----------|------|------|------|---------|--------|
| PostgreSQL | 100Gi | pd-ssd regional | $0.34 | $34.00 | $408 |
